;;;;     MEMORY ALLOCATION OVERRIDE
;;;;     ==========================
;;;;     You can override the memory allocation functions at initialization time
;;;;     like this:
;;;; 
;;;;         void* my_alloc(size_t size, void* user_data) {
;;;;             return malloc(size);
;;;;         }
;;;; 
